<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge,chrome=1">
    <meta
        name="viewport"
        content="initial-scale=1.0, maximum-scale=1.0, minimum-scale=1.0, width=device-width, user-scalable=no"/>
    <meta name="format-detection" content="telephone=no, address=no, email=no"/>
    <meta name="format-detection" content="no"/>

    <title>다이어트팜:: 엄선된 건강 식단 마켓</title>
    <style type="text/css">
        @media screen and (max-width:1079px) {
            .web_alarm {
                display: none;
            }
        }
        @media screen and (min-width:1080px) {
            .mobile_alarm {
                display: none;
            }
        #content{max-width:1080px;margin:0 auto;width:1080px;margin-bottom:100px}
        .alarm_boxes{margin-bottom:360px}    
    }
    </style>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
    <%-include(webroot + 'views/general/head') %>
    </head>

<body>
    <div class="web_alarm">
        <%-include(webroot + 'views/general/header') %>
    </div>
    <div class="mobile_alarm">
        <section class="detail_title">

            <h2>알림설정</h2>
            <a href="#" 
            value="취소"
            onclick="history.back(); return false"
        >
            <img src="/images/leftarrow_ico_my.png" style="width:17px;margin-left:10px;margin-top:2px">
        </a>
        </section>
    </div>
    <main id="content" class="alarm_content">
        <div class="alarm_web_title">
            <h2>고객센터</h2>
            <div class="contents">
                <% if (user != undefined && user.userId != '') { %>
                    <input type="hidden" id="userId" value="<%=user.userId %>">
                <% } %>
                <div class="w_sidemenu">
                    <ul>
                        <a href="notice">
                            <li class="menu">공지사항</li>
                        </a>
                        <a href="faq">
                            <li class="menu">FAQ</li>
                        </a>
                        <a href="cs-center">
                            <li class="menu">고객센터</li>
                        </a>
                        <a href="alarm">
                            <li class="clicked_menu">알림설정</li>
                        </a>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
   <div class="alarm_boxes">
      
    <div class="alarm">
        <h4>알림설정</h4>
        <div class="alarmBox">

            <h3>알림 받기</h3>
            <input type="checkbox" id="serviceAlert">
            <label for="serviceAlert">
                <span>아이콘</span></label>
        </div>

        <p class="alarmS">알림 거절 시 상품배송 및 문의 등의 정보성알림을 포함한 모든 알림을 받아보실 수 없습니다.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="alarm">
        <div class="alarmBox">
            <h3>광고성 정보 수신 동의</h3>
            <input type="checkbox" id="marketingAlert">
            <label for="marketingAlert">
                <span>아이콘</span></label>
        </div>
        <p class="alarmS">신규 서비스 및 고객 맞춤 혜택 정보를 받을 수 있습니다.</p>
    </div>
</div>

    </main>
    <script src="/js/alarm.js"></script>
</body>
</html>